<h1>Game Description</h1>

<p>
    RogueLikeGame is a endless 2D Top-view game where player need to clear stages by killing a certain amout of enemies,
    but enemies doesn't always spawn near player so you have to find them in the game generated labyrinths.

</p>
<img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/roguelikegame-64f8f.appspot.com/o/labyrinth.png?alt=media&token=e40cc6c2-3564-4c0f-bee2-9e9f50cd936f" alt="Labyrinth">
<p></p>
<p>
    You will play as a medieval ages hero. Your arsenal consists of Health Bar which represents how much
    health points does player have, obviously if health bar is at 0, player dies and Attack Indicator 
    which lets you know when you can attack.
</p>
